19
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,520
Is something wrong with my eyes?

20
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:47,080
I can't see anything.

21
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,880
That's because you're not familiar with them yet,

22
