Ding Nian.

41
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,210
Are you alright?

42
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,079
What's wrong with you?

43
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:01,360
How could you mistake a whole person for a rabbit?

44
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,200
Always bragging about having eagle eyes,

45
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,520
and you still made such a mistake.

46
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,440
If our Ding Nian loses even a single hair,

47
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:07,440
how will you make it up to her?

48
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,040
I'm sorry,

49
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,280
it's my fault.

50
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,200
